Quantum Science Toolkit
│
├── 1. User Interface Layer
│   ├── Quantum Circuit Designer GUI (Drag-and-Drop)
│   ├── CLI for Quantum Job Submission
│   └── Jupyter/Notebook Integration
│
├── 2. Application Logic Layer
│   ├── Experiment Orchestrator
│   │   ├── Job Scheduler (Local/Cloud Quantum Backends)
│   │   └── Circuit Compilation Manager
│   ├── Input/Output Handler
│   │   ├── QASM, OpenQASM, QIR Parsers
│   │   └── Validation & Preprocessing
│   └── Simulation Configurator
│       ├── Noise Models
│       └── Backend Emulator Settings
│
├── 3. Computational Core
│   ├── Quantum Algorithms Module
│   │   ├── Quantum Fourier Transform
│   │   ├── Grover’s Search
│   │   ├── Shor’s Algorithm
│   │   └── VQE/QAOA
│   ├── Quantum Simulation Engine
│   │   ├── State Vector Simulator
│   │   ├── Density Matrix Simulator
│   │   └── Stabilizer Formalism
│   └── Hybrid Quantum-Classical Routines
│       ├── Optimizers (COBYLA, SPSA, Adam)
│       └── Feedback Loop Manager
│
├── 4. Data Layer
│   ├── Quantum Datasets
│   │   ├── Hamiltonians
│   │   ├── Benchmark Circuits
│   │   └── Experimental Results Archive
│   ├── Data Management
│   │   ├── Result Serialization (HDF5, JSON)
│   │   └── Quantum Job Tracking DB
│   └── Backend Integration
│       ├── IBM Q, IonQ, Rigetti APIs
│       └── Simulated vs Real Hardware Tagging
│
└── 5. Utility & Integration Layer
    ├── Quantum Circuit Visualization (TikZ, Plotly)
    ├── Error Analysis & Mitigation Tools
    ├── Export Utilities (QASM, PNG, PDF)
    └── Plugin Support (Qiskit, Cirq, PennyLane, Braket)
